phrases: sign: I want to thank you.
Please come to the gym storage room at 12.
Why do not you try talking to him more?
Yeah, just the two of you, alone.
You might find something in him if you talk to him.
He helped you out, you know.
So he is the same as Kazehaya.
What do you think of Sanada?
I think he is a good person.
He does not avoid you or anything either, does he?
Did not you want to see Kazehaya-kun play?
I heard that he used to play baseball in middle school, and I really wanted to see him play.
I wanted to know more about Kazehaya.
See, you do not know anything about Kazehaya.
Do not think you feel the same way about him as I do.
I have been watching him since middle school.
And I talked to him whenever I had the chance.
And I made sure he would not get a girlfriend.
Yeah, I did all sorts of things.
Anyway, that is how well I know Kazehaya-kun.
It is not like I started to feel this way just yesterday.
It is always been like this.
I have always been watching him.
You cannot keep your eyes off of him.
Do not talk as if you know what you are talking about.
He would always be in your sight.
You would always be thinking about him.
You always see his face before you fall asleep.
Everything was so new to me.
I thought it was special, what I was feeling.
I think I really do not know anything.
Or if I would feel this way even if it was not Kazehaya-kun.
Or if there is anything more.
I want to know more about Kazehaya-kun and about my own feelings.
I will try talking to Sanada-kun properly.
I am going to do things my way.
I-I wonder if she did not want to watch it with me.
Kazehaya-kun must be really special to her.
She is been watching him all along.
I want to go out with him, but...
I see, so Kurumi-chan has a crush.
I never thought of that word until now.
I could not tell with your hair done differently.
I am going to go cheer for our volleyball team.
Were not you going to go cheer for Ayane-chan and Chizu-chan?
I used to be alone all the time.
Everyone around me is so nice.
It would not have been this way if even one of us was missing.
If it was not for Kazehaya-kun,
I probably would not have known how nice everyone is.
I do not know how I feel either.
I want to know my own feelings.
Maybe I will find out if I talk to Sanada-kun.
Maybe I will find some answers.
I think girls' volleyball and boys' soccer.
but it is not what you are thinking.
Did not I just say that?
That was just because I was right there.
I still feel like I wish I would caught it.
Girls' soccer and boys' softball, all good for round one.
I want to check the sports day committee schedule.
Um, never mind, I will find it myself.
I do not want to give you trouble.
The first afternoon block is clearing the field, and taking the equipment into the storage room.
If you are done, get out of here.
What is with that crazy smile?
You are Sawako-chan and Chizu-chan's friend.
You were in the same middle school as Chizu, were not you?
What are you using for foundation and stuff?
Tonight it will be a pack.
Using my sister's really expensive one.
People should not believe that stuff.
You would have to be an idiot to buy it.
Hey, you heard the rumor too, right?
Did you tell it to anyone?
I never believed it in the first place.
I just overheard a bunch of girls talking about it.
I cannot imagine you spreading rumors.
I bet it was someone who liked him, who spread that rumor.
I bet Sawako was in her way.
Even worse with me and Chizu backing her up.
So setting aside the rumor about me...
A lot of the rumors about Chizu were actually true but greatly exaggerated.
So I figure it was someone from the same school he was in.
I wonder what she would do if Kazehaya found out.
Well, you cannot really doubt someone without any evidence.
We have been talking for a while.
Maybe we should go; the game's starting.
He is got more than one.
He is in the committee too.
What are you doing afterwards, Ryu?
Oh well, I will nap outside.
Is red” a compliment to you?
Sanada-kun helped me when I was about to get hit by a ball.
He is not all bad after all.
And there is something I want to find out.
I do not really understand it myself either,
and I do not know how to explain it,
Can you hear me out once I know?
Just do what you feel is right for you.
I bet Sawako has a lot to think about.
And we have some work to do too.
I thought I said something bad to you.
S-Sanada-kun went to the gym storage room.
It is not like she is a strong rival, but she is a real pain.
Wow, why does this letter say exactly what I had in mind?
Hey, thanks for saving my life earlier.
I doubt that ball had that much force.
You are giving it to me?
Oh yeah, I wanted to talk to you.
Do you know anything about romance?
So, like, when you like someone not just as friends but as someone special
Yeah, you do not need to explain.
I think you would make a perfect couple.
I was just thinking, Kuronuma would be like, This is my work.”
Is it true that you rejected Sawako-chan before summer break?
She never confessed to me to begin with.
It is not like she likes me anyway.
She said no way” when I asked her if she wanted to go out with you.
It did not look like she cared about you earlier anyway.
You could not help but fall in love with someone, if they saved you like that.
Let us cheer her on if she likes him, okay?
Since when have you liked Yoshida-san?
How did you know she was special?
Do I have to answer logically?
She was always special to me by the time I knew it.
I cannot compare her to anyone else.
D-Does it make her special if you cannot compare her?
See, let us cheer her on.
